{"id":995,"date":"2026-01-24T21:13:52","date_gmt":"2026-01-24T21:13:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/?p=995"},"modified":"2026-03-14T05:14:48","modified_gmt":"2026-03-14T05:14:48","slug":"national-ad-council","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/national-ad-council\/","title":{"rendered":"National Ad Council"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<section class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-post-banner section-post-banner\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><div class=\"t-box t-box-a\"><h1 class=\"hg\">NATIONAL AD<br>COUNCIL<\/h1><div class=\"i-line\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-b\"><div class=\"container-studies\"><div class=\"label-studies\">FORM STUDY<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">branding<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">social media animation<\/div><\/div><div class=\"container-roles\"><div class=\"label-roles\">ROLE<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">concept<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">design<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">motion<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">compositor<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-c\"><div class=\"media-wrapper\"><div class=\"media-overlay\"><div class=\"media-overlay-placeholder--mask\"><div class=\"media-overlay-placeholder--text\">Visit Full Video<\/div><\/div><\/div><a class=\"t-media-wrapper\" href=\"https:\/\/vimeo.com\/1015558210\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><video class=\"t-media\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/jgunarto_praina_nac.mp4\" loop muted playsinline autoplay><\/video><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"section-post-detail\" class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-post-detail\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><header class=\"t-box-a post-detail__meta\"><div class=\"post-detail__heading\">(PROJECT DETAIL)<\/div><div class=\"post-info\"><div class=\"post-info__item\"><div class=\"post-info__item-background\"><\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-label\">MEDIUM<\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-value\"> 2d<\/div><\/div><div class=\"post-info__item\"><div class=\"post-info__item-background\"><\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-label\">TOOLS<\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-value\">ADOBE AFTER EFFECTS, ILLUSTRATOR, PHOTOSHOP<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/header><div class=\"t-box-b post-detail__body\"><nav class=\"post-detail__tabs\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab-dot is--active\"><\/div><ul class=\"post-detail__tab-list\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab is--active\">OVERVIEW<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">CHALLENGE<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">REFLECTION<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">SCRIPT<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">AWARD<\/div><\/ul><\/nav><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body\"><ul class=\"post-detail__tab-body-list\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item is--active\">The Ad Council has sparked social change through storytelling since 1942. We&#8217;re building on their clean, text-forward design: elevating it through motion<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">Create an exciting\/attention-grabbing animation through social media post that would appeal to young first time voters: to push them to get out and vote<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">We set clear type rules: mixing small descriptions with bold, overlapping text (to add variety and clarity). <br>What began fragmented grew to be a cohesive, minimalist piece through intentional framing.<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">Still staring at the clock? Did you know 1 in 3 adults struggle with sleep? The excessive screen time and swiping, heavy meals, and caffeine are common culprits. Lack of sleep makes you 3 times more prone to anxiety and heart risks. So make the small changes tonight. Sleep tight, reset right.<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">ADDY Student Silver Award 2025<\/div><\/ul><\/div><div class=\"post-detail__media-container\"><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ad_Council_logo_2018.svg_.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Ad_Council_logo_2018.svg_.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/nac_direction1-1-scaled-1.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/nac_direction1-1-scaled-1.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/nac_still.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/nac_still.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Screenshot-2026-01-25-at-11.36.37-am.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Screenshot-2026-01-25-at-11.36.37-am.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Screenshot-2026-01-25-at-11.37.14-am.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Screenshot-2026-01-25-at-11.37.14-am.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-post-gallery section-post-gallery\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><div class=\"t-box t-box-a\"><h2 class=\"hg\">DESIGN + motion <\/h2><div class=\"i-line\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-b\"><div class=\"caption-1\">(INFO)<\/div><div class=\"t-body\">look through the explorations we&#8217;ve done to create interesting type in a 